OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter woman's body found in flat
OL,6,FA man has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof murder after the body of a woman
OL,8,Fwas found in a flat in Stoke-on-Trent.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to an
OL,11,Faddress at Oakwell Court in Longton at
OL,12,Faround 3:30am on Sunday (July 12th).
OL,14,FThey found the woman inside, who is
OL,15,Fbelieved to be in her 20s.
OL,17,FA 30-year-old man from Stoke-on-Trent
OL,18,Fhas been arrested on suspicion of
OL,19,Fmurder and is currently in custody for
OL,20,Fquestioning.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
