OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter woman's body found in flat
OL,6,FStaffordshire Police say the woman's
OL,7,Fnext of kin have been informed and are
OL,8,Fnow being supported by specially
OL,9,Ftrained officers.
OL,11,FA scene remains at the address as
OL,12,Fpolice look for investigative
OL,13,Fopportunities to understand exactly
OL,14,Fwhat has happened.
OL,16,FThey added that there will be an
OL,17,Fincreased presence of neighbourhood
OL,18,Fofficers in the local area throughout
OL,19,Fthe day to help provide reassurance to
OL,20,Fthe local community and to gather
OL,21,Fevidence.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/3
